messages.messageBody:
I liked the Wonder Twins when I was a kid. {was the youngest to my 3
sisters by 8+ years, so I guess being a twin thing appealed to me}
Yes, I did love the smurfs too but always wondered, where the other
girls were.
Tracy {who now has the smurf song, Smurfette sings in her head. ~~~
